[color=#5b97bc][head=2]Feeling Off This Shift?[/head]
[bold] Talk to the Station Psychologist [/bold]
[/color]

Stress, trauma, burnout, paranoia — these aren't just "in your head." They're real, and they [italic]can[/italic] be treated.

Whether you've had a rough shift, lost a limb, or can't sleep after that last anomaly breach, [bold]confidential psychological support is available.[/bold]
Even chronic problems like narcolepsy can be treated.

• Private, judgment-free sessions  
• Medication available when needed  
• Walk-ins or referrals accepted  
• No cameras. No AI. No records without your consent.

[italic]Located next to Medbay. Just knock.[/italic] 
Your mind deserves as much care as your body.
